<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm busy, so I'm hanging up.</b></font>

158
00:10:16,594 --> 00:10:20,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, wait! Bunta?!</b></font>

159
00:10:20,794 --> 00:10:22,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's with him?!</b></font>

160
00:10:29,904 --> 00:10:32,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's been days!</i></b></font>

161
00:10:37,884 --> 00:10:40,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Darn! I still can't control it!</i></b></font>

162
00:10:51,824 --> 00:10:54,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm gonna be late for work!</b></font>

163
00:10:58,964 --> 00:11:01,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's that rude girl.</i></b></font>

164
00:11:11,944 --> 00:11:14,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Taiyaki</b></font>

165
00:11:11,944 --> 00:11:14,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}Fresh Baked and Delicious"</b></font>

166
00:11:15,184 --> 00:11:16,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll take six.</b></font>

167
00:11:16,784 --> 00:11:19,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Five in the bag, and I'll eat one now.</b></font>

168
00:11:19,854 --> 00:11:22,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay. That'll be 660 yen.</b></font>

169
00:11:22,354 --> 00:11:24,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Careful, it's hot.</b></font>

170
00:11:25,594 --> 00:11:27,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Delicious!</i></b></font>

171
00:11:29,364 --> 00:11:32,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, no! I'm ten yen short.</b></font>

172
00:11:32,104 --> 00:11:36,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sorry, but can I give you a 10,000 yen bill?</b></font>

173
00:11:36,134 --> 00:11:37,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's too big.</b></font>

174
00:11:37,974 --> 00:11:41,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--I don't have change for that.
--Really?</b></font>

175
00:11:45,044 --> 00:11:46,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, no...</b></font>

176
00:11:50,084 --> 00:11:52,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Take it.</b></font>

177
00:11:55,124 --> 00:11:57,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thank you! I'll pay you back later.</b></font>

178
00:11:57,624 --> 00:11:59,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's okay. It's only ten yen.</b></font>

179
00:11:59,794 --> 00:12:03,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I want to! I wouldn't feel good otherwise.</b></font>

180
00:12:03,064 --> 00:12:05,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Where can I find you?</b></font>

181
00:12:07,064 --> 00:12:10,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I work at the gas station down the street.</b></font>

182
00:12:10,574 --> 00:12:14,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I started a temp job at
the hotel where I'm staying.</b></font>

183
00:12:14,574 --> 00:12:17,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My aunt works there.</b></font>

184
00:12:17,374 --> 00:12:19,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm running an errand for her.</b></font>

185
00:12:21,514 --> 00:12:23,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sorry about the other day.</b></font>

186
00:12:23,514 --> 00:12:26,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--You're nice.
--Well...</b></font>

187
00:12:26,024 --> 00:12:28,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was actually happy,</b></font>

188
00:12:28,694 --> 00:12:33,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>because people rarely
compliment my brother's old Levin.</b></font>

189
00:12:33,694 --> 00:12:35,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's your brother's?</b></font>

190
00:12:35,694 --> 00:12:38,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't know anyone in Gunma,</b></font>

191
00:12:38,704 --> 00:12:41,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so I was feeling bored...</b></font>

192
00:12:41,704 --> 00:12:44,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...and kind of lonely.</b></font>

193
00:12:46,904 --> 00:12:48,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's be friends.</b></font>

194
00:12:48,874 --> 00:12:51,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm Kazumi Akiyama.</b></font>

195
00:12:52,944 --> 00:12:55,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Uh, I'm Itsuki Takeuchi.</b></font>

196
00:12:55,254 --> 00:12:58,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>See you soon, Itsuki.</b></font>

197
00:13:07,364 --> 00:13:09,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This sensation...</b></font>

198
00:13:09,394 --> 00:13:11,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Could it be...</b></font>

199
00:13:12,604 --> 00:13:14,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...that?!</b></font>

200
00:13:20,244 --> 00:13:23,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Akina's Eight-Six is back in action?</b></font>

201
00:13:23,014 --> 00:13:26,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kenta thinks he saw it drive by.</b></font>

202
00:13:26,784 --> 00:13:30,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He saw the "Fujiwara Tofu Shop" sign.</b></font>

203
00:13:31,624 --> 00:13:35,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wonder if he put in a new engine.</b></font>

204
00:13:35,454 --> 00:13:38,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We should find out.</b></font>

205
00:13:39,264 --> 00:13:40,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

206
00:13:46,864 --> 00:13:48,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There!</b></font>

207
00:13:48,734 --> 00:13:51,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That engine sound...</i></b></font>

208
00:14:00,144 --> 00:14:02,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Big brother, wasn't that...?</b></font>

209
00:14:02,554 --> 00:14:06,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah. He isn't used to it yet...</b></font>

210
00:14:06,884 --> 00:14:10,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...but that car's been
revived as a scary monster.</b></font>

211
00:14:21,074 --> 00:14:24,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It took you a long time. Anything happen?</b></font>

212
00:14:24,774 --> 00:14:26,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No.</b></font>

213
00:14:26,274 --> 00:14:28,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>After the deliveries,</b></font>

214
00:14:28,114 --> 00:14:30,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I drove the pass a few times.</b></font>

215
00:14:30,674 --> 00:14:32,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I used a lot of gas.</b></font>

216
00:14:32,844 --> 00:14:34,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sorry.</b></font>

217
00:14:34,684 --> 00:14:38,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't mind.</b></font>

218
00:14:38,524 --> 00:14:41,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Dad?
--Yeah?</b></font>

219
00:14:41,194 --> 00:14:44,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Cornering with this car is tough.</b></font>

220
00:14:44,394 --> 00:14:47,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What I could do before</b></font>

221
00:14:47,194 --> 00:14:49,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>isn't as easy with this car.</b></font>

222
00:14:49,464 --> 00:14:52,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's upsetting me.</b></font>

223
00:14:52,464 --> 00:14:56,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've been trying different things,
but it's not going very well.</b></font>

224
00:14:58,404 --> 00:15:00,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Good attitude.</i></b></font>

225
00:15:00,404 --> 00:15:03,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He's trying to compensate with his technique</i></b></font>

226
00:15:03,544 --> 00:15:06,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>instead of changing the suspension settings.</i></b></font>

227
00:15:06,544 --> 00:15:09,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Go ahead and struggle for a while.</i></b></font>

228
00:15:09,884 --> 00:15:13,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Trial and error is an important process.</i></b></font>

229
00:15:15,724 --> 00:15:20,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>In time, this car will improve your</i>
<i>technique without your even knowing.</i></b></font>

230
00:15:20,864 --> 00:15:24,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This car will be a tool for you</i></b></font>

231
00:15:24,064 --> 00:15:26,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>to move up to the next level.</i></b></font>

232
00:15:33,374 --> 00:15:35,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, there you are!</b></font>

233
00:15:35,614 --> 00:15:38,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey! Kazumi!</b></font>

234
00:15:39,944 --> 00:15:43,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm here to pay you back.</b></font>

235
00:15:43,454 --> 00:15:44,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Here.</b></font>

236
00:15:44,724 --> 00:15:47,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Now we're even.</b></font>

237
00:15:47,624 --> 00:15:48,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

238
00:15:48,954 --> 00:15:52,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--You really saved me yesterday!
--Oh, yeah?</b></font>

239
00:15:52,264 --> 00:15:54,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, who is that?</b></font>

240
00:15:54,764 --> 00:15:56,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>See you at 7:30!</b></font>

241
00:15:59,564 --> 00:16:02,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Who is that cutie, Itsuki?</b></font>

242
00:16:02,174 --> 00:16:05,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>She's, uh, a friend.</b></font>

243
00:16:05,004 --> 00:16:06,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A friend?!</b></font>

244
00:16:06,974 --> 00:16:10,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You said we racers don't need girls!</b></font>

245
00:16:10,044 --> 00:16:13,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What happened to "Lonely Driver Itsuki"?</b></font>

246
00:16:13,544 --> 00:16:16,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't just laugh it off!</b></font>

247
00:16:25,224 --> 00:16:26,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?</b></font>

248
00:16:29,764 --> 00:16:33,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No way. It's a Levin!</b></font>

249
00:16:33,534 --> 00:16:36,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is this really your car?</b></font>

250
00:16:36,834 --> 00:16:38,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It sure is.</b></font>

251
00:16:40,074 --> 00:16:41,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, me?</b></font>

252
00:16:41,944 --> 00:16:45,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I graduated from high school this spring,</b></font>

253
00:16:45,414 --> 00:16:47,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so I'm a year older than you.</b></font>

254
00:16:47,784 --> 00:16:50,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What did you do after you graduated?</b></font>

255
00:16:50,454 --> 00:16:53,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I got a job, sort of.</b></font>

256
00:16:53,954 --> 00:16:56,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But I didn't like it there.</b></font>

257
00:16:56,294 --> 00:17:01,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My brother often tells me
that I'm a little impatient.</b></font>

258
00:17:01,234 --> 00:17:03,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The one with the Eight-Six?</b></font>

259
00:17:03,394 --> 00:17:06,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah. You may think it's odd,</b></font>

260
00:17:06,334 --> 00:17:10,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but we were always together,
even when he went racing.</b></font>

261
00:17:10,504 --> 00:17:14,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They say he's the fastest
downhill racer in Saitama.</b></font>

262
00:17:14,674 --> 00:17:17,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wataru's downhill is--</b></font>

263
00:17:17,214 --> 00:17:20,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My big brother's name is Wataru.</b></font>

264
00:17:20,044 --> 00:17:22,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They say Wataru's downhill is sharp.</b></font>

265
00:17:25,824 --> 00:17:27,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's starting to use me</b></font>

266
00:17:27,484 --> 00:17:30,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>as an excuse to come to Gunma.</b></font>

267
00:17:30,754 --> 00:17:34,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He may be racing at some pass right now.</b></font>

268
00:17:37,934 --> 00:17:40,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sorry.</b></font>

269
00:17:40,434 --> 00:17:44,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's our policy not to race in Akagi.</b></font>

270
00:17:44,444 --> 00:17:47,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is it because I drive an Eight-Six?</b></font>

271
00:17:47,404 --> 00:17:50,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, it's because it's too easy.</b></font>

272
00:17:50,674 --> 00:17:57,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Racers in Gunma know that the
Red Suns don't race on their own turf.</b></font>

273
00:17:57,514 --> 00:17:59,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's nothing personal.</b></font>

274
00:18:00,954 --> 00:18:03,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll tell you one thing.</b></font>

275
00:18:03,724 --> 00:18:07,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We take Eight-Six racers seriously.</b></font>

276
00:18:07,724 --> 00:18:11,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Gunma's Eight-Six is a downhill specialist.</b></font>

277
00:18:11,564 --> 00:18:13,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He has never lost a race.</b></font>

278
00:18:13,734 --> 00:18:15,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?</b></font>

279
00:18:15,174 --> 00:18:17,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Against any type of car.</b></font>

280
00:18:17,474 --> 00:18:19,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Any type of car?</b></font>

281
00:18:19,804 --> 00:18:21,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Right.</b></font>

282
00:18:21,744 --> 00:18:26,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Then you're qualified to
determine if I'm faster than he is.</b></font>

283
00:18:26,744 --> 00:18:29,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--What?
--It's okay, Kenta.</b></font>

284
00:18:29,414 --> 00:18:31,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We don't race here.</b></font>

285
00:18:33,824 --> 00:18:35,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't know who you are,</b></font>

286
00:18:35,654 --> 00:18:39,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but come back in ten years if
you want to talk trash to Keisuke.</b></font>

287
00:18:51,004 --> 00:18:52,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Fine, then.</b></font>

288
00:19:05,184 --> 00:19:09,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I hate to do this, but you've left me no choice.</i></b></font>

289
00:19:14,964 --> 00:19:18,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>If you're that desperate,</i>
<i>I'll play with you a little!</i></b></font>

290
00:19:20,464 --> 00:19:22,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That's more like it.</i></b></font>

291
00:19:22,404 --> 00:19:26,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Please teach that rude jerk a lesson!</i></b></font>

292
00:19:35,184 --> 00:19:38,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That sound... it's a turbo!</i></b></font>

293
00:19:41,424 --> 00:19:44,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He followed me out of the corner.</i></b></font>

294
00:19:44,254 --> 00:19:47,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That car's power isn't ordinary.</i></b></font>

295
00:19:47,994 --> 00:19:50,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Is it really an Eight-Six?</i></b></font>

296
00:19:57,434 --> 00:19:59,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I don't know how powerful it is,</i></b></font>

297
00:19:59,904 --> 00:20:04,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>but that much power will impede his control.</i></b></font>

298
00:20:04,274 --> 00:20:07,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That car is like a loose cannon,</i></b></font>

299
00:20:07,284 --> 00:20:10,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>but he's controlling it!</i></b></font>

300
00:20:10,554 --> 00:20:13,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I just can't keep up!</i></b></font>

301
00:20:13,524 --> 00:20:15,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Darn!</i></b></font>

302
00:20:18,694 --> 00:20:22,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I don't know as much as my brother,</i></b></font>

303
00:20:22,194 --> 00:20:26,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>but this guy is very skilled.</i>
<i>I shouldn't mess around.</i></b></font>

304
00:20:26,804 --> 00:20:30,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Get serious... or I'll pass you!</i></b></font>

305
00:20:34,304 --> 00:20:37,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Man, this doesn't look good.</b></font>

306
00:20:37,714 --> 00:20:41,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Luckily, we weren't going too fast.</b></font>

307
00:20:41,044 --> 00:20:42,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

308
00:20:42,414 --> 00:20:45,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I should put a warning reflector up.</b></font>

309
00:20:45,224 --> 00:20:47,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'd hate for another car to crash into us.</b></font>

310
00:20:47,884 --> 00:20:49,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

311
00:21:19,384 --> 00:21:24,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Whenever I turned around</i></b></font>

312
00:21:24,294 --> 00:21:29,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>There was always that</i>
<i>unchanging smile of yours</i></b></font>

313
00:21:29,564 --> 00:21:34,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It was there on days when</i>
<i>I was too tired to go on</i></b></font>

314
00:21:34,234 --> 00:21:43,044
